room_title: Escape room "Toy Shop: SVU" by The Escape Artist KC in Kansas City
room_address: 408 B. East 18th St. Kansas City, MO 64108
room_description:
Notorious Bad-Boy Knuckles Kat Jr. considered by local police to be Public Enemy Number One as the leader of The Trash Can Syndicate and Boss of the Neverland Mafia is suspected in the catnapping of Never-Ever-Land's favorite socialite. 
Your team of detectives is brought in to investigate before tragedy strikes and Knuckles can continue his reign of terror.  
Can your group figure out what's going on in time?
